                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18141026-156-off902 t18141026-156-crimeloc905"></join>. On Saturday, the 8th of October, about three in the afternoon, I was coming out of my back parlour into the shop; I observed the prisoner Mary Allen looking at some shoes that were hung at the door post, having lost some things previous, I put myself in a situation to see her without being seen; in the space of a minute 
